ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 250, Prince Edward Island
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 250 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND with respect to the post-tropical storm that occurred from September 23 to 25, 2022.
